jzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"43","text":"- Profiláctica:","guid":"fp0RCX2bANFjJAOojEX2iQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"- Insuficiencia medular: <10×10⁹/L","guid":"Zg2xcmwv1L-8WVOlX6Jpow","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"- Con factores de riesgo: <20×10⁹/L","guid":"YYqNpPux0ueC8Ks4huXA4w","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"- Punción lumbar: <50×10⁹/L","guid":"OzQ2nAMo8iB8E2NAyfzzag","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"- Anestesia peridural: <80×10⁹/L","guid":"_ag4_oEKIJJ3g25lsRB8gg","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"- Procedimientos invasivos con riesgo: <50×10⁹/L","guid":"0cWvhdpxTWRmkAQQjmX5-A","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"48","text":"- Cirugías mayores electivas: <50×10⁹/L","guid":"MHkEYT1Gbdd1Hr-giEiCcA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"48","text":"- Cirugías neuroquirúrgicas/oculares: <100×10⁹/L","guid":"kOaubYIh4XgQTxqmSZXkiQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"39","text":"###\\NREFRACTARIEDAD\\NPLAQUETARIA","guid":"60uuclMXg4jq-RDYcNeBLQ","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Ausencia de respuesta después de 2 transfusiones ABO compatibles","guid":"7UTQ3e3-8xz2mS5CHY0XIg","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"- Número de plaquetas\\Ntransfundidas (↑PP)","guid":"FTpOtqRZJ2nZW5gWTecKWQ","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- Valor esperado en adulto post transfusión = la ↑PP = 7.5 x 10¹¹, después de una hora de la transfusión","guid":"YV7abJdA0lEhlQbGhbNC-Q","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"- Se recomiendan estudios diagnósticos si tras pocas de trasladar las plaquetas transfundidas se\\Nobserva un \"fallo demostrado\", si estos no están asociados a sepsis y estado clínico del paciente","guid":"cvZ7nJGdzKrmjY3ncOZoFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"56","text":"- Causas inmunológicas: aloanticuerpos, complejos inmunes, etc.","guid":"i8_0MI82kGuTHlsOjvDvuQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"56","text":"- Causas no in